Engage multiple stakeholders for access and analysis of data sets;
Use historic data for predictive modeling and operations research;
Join/merge multiple databases across our field equipment portfolio;
Create of a new visualizations and tools to optimize our field equipment portfolio;
Determine and quantify data quality issues (i.e. amount of missing data);
Provide recommendations to improve data quality and use cases.

